longBusinessSummary: VNUE, Inc. operates as a music technology company. It provides a suite of products and services that monetize music for artists, labels, radio stations, venues, restaurants, gyms, bars, and other businesses. The company also offers Set.fm/DiscLive Network, a digital live music distribution consumer app platform that allows users to download and purchase through their mobile devices; and provides physical collectible products that are recorded and sold at shows, as well as online through the company's partner DiscLive Network. In addition, it provides Soundstr, a music identification and rights management cloud platform that track and audit public performances of music; and offers collectible products, such as CDs, USB drives, and laminates. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in New York, New York.
